00:59:52.040 --> 00:59:53.440
Tu veux te venger ?

01:00:27.680 --> 01:00:29.200
Kae, ça va ?

01:00:30.520 --> 01:00:31.520
Je vais bien!

01:00:31.960 --> 01:00:33.080
